title: The Royble
description:
The Greatest Story Ever Told Badly.

A cross between the bible, hitch hikers guide to the galaxy and The Inbetweeners.

In the beginning Roy created Aylesbury and the earth, oddly millions of years before he, and his evil twin brother Rastas are born. 
Roy and Rastas are separated at birth when a, presumably, evil nurse kidnaps Rastas.
As a child, despite being unaware of his divinity, Roy realizes he is different. He has an amazing gift - the ability to pack bags full of food. Quite well. 
Despite RoyÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s amazing bag-packing powers his divinity is not discovered until 1984, 17 years after he was born. Tim, an Aylesbury schoolboy, meets him in a local factory. Roy commands Time to find him 12 disciples, plus one substitute. And to worship him, and stuff. 

The Royble contains all the letters of the alphabet, even rubbish ones like 'w'.
